u003Cspan class=\"line\">\u003Cspan style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/code>\u003C/pre>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"performance-considerations\">Performance Considerations\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Use \u003Ccode>transform\u003C/code> and \u003Ccode>opacity\u003C/code> for best performance\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Avoid animating \u003Ccode>width\u003C/code>, \u003Ccode>height\u003C/code>, or \u003Ccode>margin\u003C/code>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Use \u003Ccode>will-change\u003C/code> sparingly\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Test on low-end devices\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>The key to great dark theme animations is subtlety combined with impact. Use motion to guide the eye, not distract it.\u003C/p>",{"headings":179,"localImagePaths":195,"remoteImagePaths":196,"frontmatter":197,"imagePaths":200},[180,183,186,189,192],{"depth":181,"slug":182,"text":45},1,"gamers-outreach",{"depth":31,"slug":184,"text":185},"the-float-animation","The Float Animation",{"depth":31,"slug":187,"text":188},"glow-effects","Glow Effects",{"depth":31,"slug":190,"text":191},"gradient-animations","Gradient Animations",{"depth":31,"slug":193,"text":194},"performance-considerations","Performance Considerations",[],[],{"title":45,"description":169,"pubDate":198,"tags":199},["Date","2023-12-25T00:00:00.000Z"],[172],[]]